{
  "stem": "22910.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I figured there are other ways of, of taking on an identity, not by killing yourself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they gave some soup-- and this too afterwards I realized-- soup where I come from meant nice very watery soup.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, because you had a meal afterwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was just like chicken soup, right?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That doesn't have anything in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You were smart enough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You put all kinds of other things in it, but no, of course not.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So this had all kinds of things in it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And who wants soup look like this?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We're not used to soup like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I ate it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I ate it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were just wandering around, and every morning, sel appel at 5 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sel appel, which was counting time-- you know, the time for counting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Stand in line, five to, to a line being counted-- counted again, counted again.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the weather there is absolutely the most horrible weather ever anyplace-- rainy and muddy and cold.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "May, this was May already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very cold, and we of course were cold anyway because we only had a dress, not anything to cover ourselves, not anything to put on the-- above the planks of the beds.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we were always cold and standing in the rain and not food and nothing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, if you didn't stay in the line, then somebody came with a whip and whipped you, and just like a nightmare-- just an absolute nightmare.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this was our life at that point.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we didn't have any idea where my parents were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You were with someone you knew?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just my sister.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And somehow we got into a barrack where no one from our town was there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this went on.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was no work.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
